{"type": "article", "id": 21691, "title": "“cassia” by petra krausova", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-02T07:34:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140517BjS1aZMWmJGpzRq2.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是捷克灯具品牌 LASVIT 在巴黎家博会上带来的一款吊灯，仿佛在夜空中绽放的花朵。这些灯是经过吹制而成的，使用五种不同的玻璃材料，毛玻璃、不透明玻璃、磨砂玻璃、透明玻璃以及金属喷漆的玻璃，高高低低悬挂着，让吊灯呈现出一种富有变化的晶莹感，也展现出吹制技术。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140515buqnfPmDN0spYjS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140515PTjJ8Un7gb2ENmFH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65770171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140516VL5m9tFMlBYaDXZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606140516rXTPRs7NB9bmpKCt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}